                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">这个作者很厉害，知道读者喜欢听什么，不爱听什么，技术性的问题一概不讲，八卦内幕（不敏感的）尤其多。算是Self promoting之作吧~</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="936237553">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-936237553" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-936237553" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="936237553">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/honeyclover/">clover</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-08-12</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">其实不只是和中国打交道，而是在说怎么做才能成大事</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

