                Now, as China has grown to be one of the world's largest economies, many Americans wonder:Why help a competitor?<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>Simple: because Chinese issues are global issues that affect the US too.<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>Furthermore, a relationship of mutual investment between the two countries is mutually beneficial.
