              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/43131659/" class="">Chapter One: At the Purple Light Pavilion</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Ritz-Carlton/" class=" " title="居家男人">居家男人</a>
                (如切如磋，如琢如磨)
              
